quran[71]{c,v,t}:
  80,1,Iye anachita matsinya ndi kuyang’ana kumbali
  80,2,Chifukwa munthu wakhungu anadza kwa iye
  80,3,Ndipo iwe ungadziwe bwanji kuti mwina angadziyeretse
  80,4,Kapena iye adzalandira chenjezo ndipo chenjezo likanamupindulira kanthu kena
  80,5,Koma iye amene amadziyesa kuti sasowa kanthu
  80,6,Ameneyo ndiye amene uli naye ndi chidwi
  80,7,Kodi uli nazo chiani ngati iye sadziyeretsa
  80,8,Koma kwa iye amene amakuthamangira
  80,9,Ndipo iye amaopa
  80,10,Iwe siudamulabadire ayi
  80,11,Iyayi! Ndithudi chimenechi ndi chikumbutso
  80,12,Muloleni aliyense amene afuna kuti achilabadire
  80,13,Ichi chidalembedwa m’Buku la Mulungu lolemekezeka
  80,14,Loyeretsedwa ndi losungidwa bwino ndi loyera
  80,15,M’manja mwa Alembi
  80,16,Wolemekezeka ndipo womvera
  80,17,Atembereredwe munthu! Kodi ndi chiani chili kumuletsa kuthokoza
  80,18,Kodi Iye adamulenga kuchokera ku chiyani
  80,19,"Kuchokera ku dontho la umuna, Iye adamulenga ndipo adamukonza bwino"
  80,20,Ndipo Iye adamukonzera iye njira yapafupi
  80,21,Ndipo amamupha ndi kumusunga m’manda
  80,22,Ndithudi Iye adzamudzutsa monga momwe afunira
  80,23,"Iyayi, koma munthu sanachite zimene Iye adamulamulira"
  80,24,Mulekeni munthu kuti aganize za chakudya chake
  80,25,Kuti Ife timagwetsa mvula yambiri
  80,26,Ndipo timaphwanya nthaka
  80,27,"Ndipo Ife Al-Takwir\t641 timameretsa njere"
  80,28,Mphesa ndi Msipu
  80,29,"Mitengo ya mafuta, ndi mitengo ya tende"
  80,30,Ndi minda imene ili ndi mitengo yambiri
  80,31,Ndi mitengo ya zipatso ndi msipu
  80,32,Chakudya cha inu ndi ziweto zanu
  80,33,Koma pamene kulira kogonthetsa mkhutu kudzamveka
  80,34,Patsiku limene munthu adzakana m’bale wake
  80,35,Amai ake ndi bambo ake
  80,36,Mkazi wake ndi ana ake
  80,37,"Chifukwa aliyense patsiku limeneli, adzakhala otangwanika ndi mavuto ake"
  80,38,Patsiku limeneli padzakhala nkhope zambiri zowala
  80,39,Zosekerera ndi zachimwemwe chifukwa cha nkhani yabwino
  80,40,Ndipo pa tsikuli padzakhala nkhope zina zokutidwa ndi fumbi
  80,41,M’dima udzakuta iwo
  80,42,Awa adzakhala anthu osakhulupirira ndi ochita zoipa
  81,1,Pamene dzuwa lidzavundikiridwa
  81,2,Ndi pamene nyenyezi zidzagwa pansi
  81,3,Ndi pamene mapiri adzachotsedwa
  81,4,Ndi pamene ngamila zabele zizakhala zosasamalidwa
  81,5,Ndi nyama za m’tchire zidzasonkhanitsidwa pamodzi
  81,6,Ndi pamene nyanja zidzayatsidwa moto kapena zidzasefukira
  81,7,Ndi pamene mizimu idzakumanitsidwa ndi matupi awo
  81,8,"Ndi pamene mwana wa mkazi wa mng’ono, amene adaundilidwa wa moyo adzafunsidwa"
  81,9,Chifukwa chimene anamuphera
  81,10,Ndi pamene mabuku olembamo ntchito za munthu aliyense adzatulutsidwa
  81,11,Ndi pamene kumwamba kudzafafanizidwa ndi kuchotsedwa ku malo ake
  81,12,Ndi pamene Gahena idzatenthetsedwa kwambiri
  81,13,Ndi pamene Paradiso idzafikitsidwa pafupi
  81,14,Ndithudi munthu aliyense adzadziwa chimene adachita
  81,15,"Motero, ndithudi, Ine ndili kulumbira pali nyenyezi zimene zimalowa"
  81,16,Ndi pali maiko zimene zimayenda mofulumira ndi kudzibisa okha
  81,17,Ndi pali usiku pamene uchoka
  81,18,Ndipalim’mawapamenekulikucha
  81,19,Ndithudi awa ndi Mau a Mtumwi wolemekezeka
  81,20,"Mwini mphamvu amene amalemekezedwa ndi Ambuye, Mwini Mpando wa Chifumu"
  81,21,Amamveredwa ndi wokhulupirika
  81,22,Ndipo m’bale wanu uyu si wa misala ayi
  81,23,"Ndipo, ndithudi, iye adamuona iye mu mlengalenga"
  81,24,Iye sabisa zinthu zosaoneka
  81,25,Ndipo zimene alankhula sizochokera kwa Satana wotembereredwa
  81,26,Kodi inu muli kupita kuti
  81,27,Ndithudi ichi si china chilichonse ayi koma chikumbutso kwa anthu a mitundu yonse
  81,28,Kwa aliyense wa inu amene afuna kuyenda moongoka
  81,29,"Koma inu simungathe kutero pokhapokha ndi chifuniro cha Mulungu, Ambuye wa zolengedwe zonse"